The paper discusses learning from temporal data and proposes a new approach based on the principle of Least Cognitive Action, which involves differential equations. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), systems and control (cs.SY), and information theory (cs.IT).
